        <Parent_String>densimeters [300196387], quantity measuring devices [300195706], measuring devices for extent [300195701], measuring devices (instruments) [300207870], Measuring Devices (hierarchy name) [300207851], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
